Class UnderlineListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.v4.runtime.BaseErrorListener
      • UnderlineListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.ANTLRErrorListener

    public class UnderlineListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.BaseErrorListener
    An error listener for printing information about syntax errors This ErrorListener should be added to a parser. Whenever a syntax error occurs, the syntaxError() method is called. The follows follows set for the previous token is printed and the offending token is underlined.
